# CodeCortex indexing

## When to use

- Stale, partial, or unknown `freshness`
- First-time setup, `cortex watch`, vector-index, background jobs

## Workflow

1. `check_health` → `index_status` (+ `vector_index_status` if semantic search needed)
2. `explain_index_freshness` / `diagnose` when repairing
3. Repair: `add_code_to_graph` (default `force: true`) or `cortex index <repo> --force`
4. Poll `list_jobs` / `check_job_status` for background work

## MUST NOT

- Run expensive graph analysis while index is stale (repair first).

